00:07:26,324 --> 00:07:33,327
to name these. But we also realized that we did not really know the Edossians and their concerns.

106
00:07:34,808 --> 00:07:40,111
Not that we did not have employee well-being at heart, but since we were all working together

107
00:07:40,151 --> 00:07:48,955
in one place, we assumed we knew each other, which is totally wrong. As a first step and

108
00:07:49,015 --> 00:07:52,517
based on the results of these surveys, we implemented some quick actions.

109
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:58,542
Setting up studio and project showcases for more visibility.

110
00:07:59,562 --> 00:08:01,263
