213
00:15:03,017 --> 00:15:11,322
Only 6% of Edossians are not able to have a work rhythm that allows them to finish their work week without being exhausted.

214
00:15:13,143 --> 00:15:17,805
And only 7% of Edossians are less productive with this new program.

215
00:15:19,064 --> 00:15:20,644
So at the end, it's great results.

216
00:15:21,185 --> 00:15:22,365
I'm very, very happy.

217
00:15:23,605 --> 00:15:26,946
It's very positive, but we still have to adjust

218
00:15:27,126 --> 00:15:29,746
and test new things to make sure

219
00:15:29,766 --> 00:15:32,447
that everyone feel comfortable at work

220
00:15:33,227 --> 00:15:37,868
and have a well-balanced private life, of course.

221
00:15:38,348 --> 00:15:40,389
So all the Eidosians have at the heart

222
00:15:40,649 --> 00:15:41,989
the studio of performance,

223
00:15:42,949 --> 00:15:44,590
because Eidos is an ecosystem

224
00:15:44,730 --> 00:15:47,270
where people are linked around the same values.

225
00:15:48,939 --> 00:15:53,341
valued as human beings and others send the decisions that affect them.

226
00:15:58,184 --> 00:16:05,928
In conclusion, our learning shows that making the spectrum complex and heavy

227
00:16:06,468 --> 00:16:11,250
by adding more managers as the company grows should not be the first action.

228
00:16:13,489 --> 00:16:16,490
Preparing for growth by building a culture of accountability,

229
00:16:17,190 --> 00:16:21,491
participation without silos can yield more impressive results.

230
00:16:23,831 --> 00:16:26,271
There is nothing stronger than collective intelligence

231
00:16:26,912 --> 00:16:29,752
and the structure and perpetual adjustment according to needs.

232
00:16:31,972 --> 00:16:35,813
With an ever-increasing collective participation that

233
00:16:35,933 --> 00:16:38,414
unites us, we continue to learn at Eidos,

234
00:16:38,654 --> 00:16:40,594
explore, and test new avenues.

235
00:16:41,498 --> 00:16:43,419
which I hope to share with you next year.

