00:22:19,666 --> 00:22:24,347
And we barely knew how many people were in the company

324
00:22:24,447 --> 00:22:25,687
from a global perspective.

325
00:22:26,027 --> 00:22:28,688
And I'm talking about the general population of SIE.

326
00:22:30,108 --> 00:22:31,348
So we were data starved.

327
00:22:32,613 --> 00:22:36,237
The US, they had their own DE&I strategy.

328
00:22:36,858 --> 00:22:38,540
Europe, their own strategy.

329
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:43,225
Japan, they addressed strategy, DE&I in their own way.

330
00:22:44,747 --> 00:22:46,789
And our executive leadership was fine

331
00:22:46,889 --> 00:22:48,931
