00:23:06,245 --> 00:23:06,985
which are global.

336
00:23:08,074 --> 00:23:09,395
So how did this play out?

337
00:23:10,235 --> 00:23:13,578
Well, what we observed was there was no incentive

338
00:23:13,618 --> 00:23:16,699
for middle management to advocate for DE&I

339
00:23:16,820 --> 00:23:20,542
or even to participate or even encourage participation

340
00:23:20,582 --> 00:23:21,663
from their subordinates.

341
00:23:22,403 --> 00:23:26,546
And what that meant was there was no DE&I movement globally.

342
00:23:27,866 --> 00:23:32,729
So pre-pandemic, there were less than 3% of black employees

