00:23:50,710 --> 00:23:53,352
And if you take into consideration

350
00:23:54,553 --> 00:23:56,235
all the population of SIE,

351
00:23:56,495 --> 00:23:58,316
well, I graduated to a unicorn.

352
00:23:58,736 --> 00:24:00,918
Because sprinkled throughout the organization,

