00:26:46,605 --> 00:26:49,487
Written as a response to George Floyd's killing,

397
00:26:50,247 --> 00:26:54,749
John Platt, who was the first black chairman and CEO

398
00:26:55,149 --> 00:26:57,570
of Sony ATV Music Publishing,

399
00:26:58,330 --> 00:27:01,032
wrote an article called A Change Must Come.

400
00:27:02,332 --> 00:27:04,793
And in addition to that provocative open letter,

